                  <summary><p>A multi-text manuscript containing four poems praising the Goddess Māriyammāṉ:
<list rend="numbered">
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Muttumāriyammaṉ Pēril Vārṉippu</title> (U2).</item>
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Māriyammaṉ Pēril Tālāṭṭu</title> (U3).</item>
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Māriyammaṉ Pēril Aṭaikkalapaṟṟu</title> (U4) in 10 stanzas.</item>
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Māriyammaṉ Pēril Uñcal</title> (U5) in 10 stanzas.</item>
</list></p>
<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (October 2020).</p>
<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p> 
  
   
  

